h assistance from A.J.M.. A.G. and M.L. implemented OPTIMADE server for OQMD provider with assistance from V.H., S.G., A.Me., and L.T. contributed to the implementation of the OPTIMADE::Filter Perl library for the syntactical analysis of the OPTIMADE filter language. M.Schei. implemented the OPTIMADE server for the NOMAD provider with contributions from F.M. C.T., C.O., P.C., M.E., F.Ro., and S.C. implemented the OPTIMADE server for the AFLOW provider. A.V. contributed to the long-term maintenance of the COD, to make it suitable for presentation via the OPTIMADE API.</p>
